data.description: A comfortable home that's in Move-Right-In condition in the heart of Arvada! New carpet, new paint throughout, mature landscaping, come and see this bright and inviting home. The back yard and deck are spacious and usable, including a large storage shed for gardening. Recently remodeled kitchen, stainless fridge, gas range! Great North Denver location, terrific access to local parks, Lake Arbor and walking trails, commuting routes (Hwy 36), Old Town Arvada, Westminster City Center & Light Rail!
